{"tid":269150,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（求開解） 拍左3年半拖 係上個月散左","createTime":"2017-06-03T14:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T04:18:57.000Z","uid":120923,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7058344521f509484ba8e921934c7a91138c0d53","tid":269150,"uid":120923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"同個ex已經分左手一個月<br />\n原因我諗係佢同我一齊個陣已經有同第個傾緊wts發展緊（比人帽左）<br />\n而奈左又冇新鮮感<br />\n分左手有後路比自己行<br />\n所以佢可以好快放低我<br />\n而我被分手就頭一個星期喊到懵左咁<br />\n食野又食唔到 做乜都冇精神<br />\n知道自己已經冇可能再同返佢一齊<br />\n因為岩分手個陣要挽回既都挽回左<br />\n道理我都明<br />\n但係個心放唔低佢<br />\n訓覺又成日發夢夢到佢同佢好返<br />\n起身成個人個心情就會差曬咁<br />\n試過搵過第個女既出街分散下自己心情<br />\n但自己根本冇心情再拍拖<br />\n覺得再經營一段感情已經好辛苦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd07007534b0419a0bdb519d2389ab36ac385da7","tid":269150,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"Telegram me"},{"pid":"4c43cfc6d21c492f950ecb7bf95523f2929f79e4","tid":269150,"uid":120923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:41:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Telegram me</blockquote><br />\n你id係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1f149e97d7146e0bdd0fb4651353ac02d7c55c","tid":269150,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Telegram me</blockquote><br />\n你id係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ngowithme852"},{"pid":"1a494f12dddb0c892efb57aa053938774ca88183","tid":269150,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82169a6fe01235074939cc43f9bc42a4b57ed7b","tid":269150,"uid":120923,"like":0,